  [1]: https://www.php.net/manual/en/function.str-replace.php

Try this:

    $file = fopen(&quot;mods/test.csv&quot;,&quot;r&quot;);
    $search = array();
    $replace = array();
    while (($csv = fgetcsv($file)) !== false) {
